OL,3,CLeading candidate for WRU Director of
OL,4,CRugby emerges
OL,6,FDave Reddin is the leading candidate
OL,7,Fto become the Welsh Rugby Union's new
OL,8,FDirector of Rugby, ITV Wales
OL,9,Funderstands.
OL,11,FWith 30 years of experience in elite
OL,12,Fsport, Reddin has held major roles in
OL,13,FEnglish rugby and football.
OL,15,FHe was the fitness coach on Clive
OL,16,FWoodward's backroom staff when England
OL,17,Fwon the Rugby World Cup in 2003.
