OL,3,CLeading candidate for WRU Director of
OL,4,CRugby emerges
OL,6,FThe former head coach described Reddin
OL,7,Fas playing "an absolutely pivotal role
OL,8,Fin creating our success both on and
OL,9,Foff the pitch".
OL,11,FWoodward also added that Reddin's
OL,12,Ffingerprints are "all over" some of
OL,13,Fthe biggest achievements in British
OL,14,Fsports' and called him "one of the
OL,15,Fbest I've ever worked with".
OL,17,FFollowing the World Cup triumph,
OL,18,FReddin received an MBE in 2004.
