OL,6,FIn 2008, he was appointed as Head of
OL,7,FPerformance Services at the British
OL,8,FOlympic Association. In this role, he
OL,9,F'led and implemented a new standard of
OL,10,Fperformance support' for Team GB
OL,11,Fathletes at London 2012.
OL,13,FHis next major role came at the FA,
OL,14,Fwhere he was the Head of Team Strategy
OL,15,Fand Performance for the men's and
OL,16,Fwomen's senior national sides.
