OL,4,CRugby emerges
OL,6,FDuring his five years in the role up
OL,7,Fto 2019, he worked closely with then-
OL,8,Fmanager Gareth Southgate, who credits
OL,9,FReddin with helping his development
OL,10,Fand challenging his "thinking in many
OL,11,Fareas".
OL,13,FWhen he left the FA, the then CEO
OL,14,FMartin Glenn said: "He (Reddin) has
OL,15,Fhelped to lay the foundations of the
OL,16,Fmodern day England set-up at St.
OL,17,FGeorge's Park, with elite performance
OL,18,Fat its heart."
