OL,6,F"The results have been clear to see
OL,7,Facross all of our teams and his
OL,8,Fmeticulous attention to detail has
OL,9,Fallowed us to identify, embrace and
OL,10,Fimplement new ways of working."
OL,12,FWRU Chief Executive Abi Tierney had
OL,13,Fhoped to announce the new Director of
OL,14,FRugby by the end of March.
OL,16,FAn official announcement is yet to
OL,17,Fmaterialise but ITV Wales understands
OL,18,FReddin is in pole position.
