OL,3,CLeading candidate for WRU Director of
OL,4,CRugby emerges
OL,6,FThe post has been vacant since Nigel
OL,7,FWalker left the Union in December,
OL,8,Fwith Interim Performance Director Huw
OL,9,FBevan filling the role on a temporary
OL,10,Fbasis.
OL,12,FOver the last few months, the WRU has
OL,13,Finsisted that the new Director of
OL,14,FRugby is a critical appointment. The
OL,15,Frole holds key responsibilities,
OL,16,Fincluding overseeing all rugby
OL,17,Factivity in Wales including the senior
OL,18,Fmen's and women's national sides.
