OL,3,CLeading candidate for WRU Director of
OL,4,CRugby emerges
OL,6,FFirst on the new Director of Rugby's
OL,7,Fagenda will be hiring a new head coach
OL,8,Ffor the senior men's national team.
OL,10,FJac Morgan's side are on a record
OL,11,Flosing run of 17 defeats.
OL,13,FCardiff Rugby head coach Matt Sherratt
OL,14,Fcoached Wales on a temporary basis
OL,15,Fagainst Ireland, Scotland and England
OL,16,Fin the Six Nations following Warren
OL,17,FGatland's departure mid-way through
OL,18,Fthe Six Nations.
