OL,6,FMeanwhile, Sean Lynn's tenure as head
OL,7,Fcoach of the women's senior side got
OL,8,Funderway a fortnight ago but Wales
OL,9,Fhave lost their opening games of the
OL,10,FSix Nations against Scotland and
OL,11,FEngland. Later this year, they'll face
OL,12,FCanada, Fiji and Scotland at the Rugby
OL,13,FWorld Cup.
